examples.example: 妈妈今天做的卤鸭掌味道真是太绝了。

translate.english: The spiced duck feet made by mom today tastes really excellent.

examples.example: 我最爱吃的食物之一就是美味的鸭掌。

translate.english: One of my favorite foods is the delicious duck feet.

examples.example: 我和朋友一起分享了美味的鸭掌，大家都很开心。

translate.english: I shared delicious duck feet with my friends and everyone was very happy.
